        <mxCell id="qZWEmjuA36gEhOPuAmIH-55" parent="1" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" value="乘客、司机：注册、聊天&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;乘客：输入上下车地点，&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;显示车辆、预计价格、等待时间&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;乘客：下单&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;司机：展示乘客信息、上下车地点&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;司机：接单或拒绝&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;乘客：显示司机位置和预计到达时间&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;乘客：可取消、可查看行程&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;司机：提供导航&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;司机：开始结束行程&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;乘客：支付&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;司机：结算、查看行程&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(102, 102, 0), rgb(162, 162, 74));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&l